title: Mel Robbins interview and more
itunes:title: Mel Robbins interview and more
description:
Today on the show we has author and lawyer Mel Robbins stop by where she breaks Down "The High 5 Habit", Overcoming Envy, Jealousy & Self-Rejection. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man that runs into woods after breaking into house, and calls 911 when he gets lost. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
